rl away with your friends don't be surprised if you are approached for business in a bar. but on the whole the Palace is very very good and yes you look at the palm building site but thats dubai. I wont be rushing back to dubai but its not because of the royal mirage as its a fantastic spot in the middle of buliding site that resembles a growing london docklands.	
